### GET /commerceDocuments{{Oraclecpqo Commerce Process}}{{Transaction}}

This endpoint retrieves commerce documents related to the specified commerce process and transaction.

#### Request

- No request body is required for this endpoint.


#### Response

The response for this request is a JSON object representing the commerce documents. The schema for the response can be documented as follows:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "documentId": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "documentType": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "documentName": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "documentUrl": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "createdDate": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "date-time"
    },
    "lastUpdatedDate": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "date-time"
    }
  }
}

 ```

